des: In todays world, theres so little time left for hobbies or just recreation... And if you have a baby, you stop noticing everything around you. I assure you, you can learn to find time for your favorite activities! In our daily rubric you will find all the necessary tips for organizing your time, baby care, tips for taking care of yourself and much more. This tool does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only, and is not a substitute for professional medical advice, treatment or diagnosis. Call your doctor to receive medical advice. If you think you may have a medical emergency, please dial your local emergency response phone number.
